ry tickets for family and friends  Shuttle Service will be available between Moody Hall and Cameron Hall for those attending Commencement  There will be a ticket turn in booth outside Cameron Hall for those who have extra tickets  These tickets are then redistributed to those who need an extra ticket on a first come  first served basis  We also anticipate simulcasting this event in the Gillis Theater of the Center for Leadership and Ethics on Post   This event will be live streamed at www vmi edu livestream for those family members unable to attend All Attending Commencement All attending Commencement are reminded that tickets are required  Each graduating cadet will receive a certain number of complimentary tickets for family and friends  Shuttle Service will be available between Moody Hall and Cameron Hall for those attending Commencement  There will be a ticket turn in booth outside Cameron Hall for those who have extra tickets  These tickets are then redistributed to those who need an extra ticket on a first come  first served basis  We also anticipate simulcasting this event in the Gillis Theater of the Center for Leadership and Ethics on Post   This event will be live streamed at www vmi edu livestream for those family members unable to attend All attending Commencement are reminded that tickets are required  Each graduating cadet will receive a certain number of complimentary tickets for family and friends All attending Commencement Shuttle Service will be available between Moody Hall and Cameron Hall for those attending Commencement There will be a ticket turn in booth outside Cameron Hall for those who have extra tickets  These tickets are then redistributed to those who need an extra ticket on a first come  first served basis We also anticipate simulcasting this event in the Gillis Theater of the Center for Leadership and Ethics on Post   This event will be live streamed at www vmi edu livestream for those family members unable to attend www vmi edu livest